-- No bomb found at Mexico bourse, operations normal
-- 
-- Mon Aug 23, 2010 3:57pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/08/23/us-mexico-bombthreat-idUSTRE67M4EI20100823

 

 MEXICO CITY  (Reuters) - No bomb has been found at the headquarters of Mexico City's stock exchange and operations at the bourse continue normally, said Roberto Gavaldon, a communications official at the exchange. 

 An anonymous bomb threat was called into Mexico City police earlier on Monday, Gavaldon said. (Reporting by  Missy Ryan ; Writing by  Robert Campbell )